{"name": "piiscanner", "metadata": {"name": "PIIScanner", "version": "0.1.1", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": "https://github.com/devankit01/pii_scanner", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["presidio-analyzer"], "summary": "A library for scanning Personally Identifiable Information (PII).", "upload_time": 1733997809}, "documentation": ["# PII Scanner\n\nA library for scanning Personally Identifiable Information (PII) from text.\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install pii_scanner\n```\n\n## Usage \n\n```bash\nfrom pii_scanner.scanner import PIIScanner\n\n# Create an instance of the scanner\npii_scanner = PIIScanner()\n\n# Sample data containing PII\ndata = [\n    \"Ankit Gupta\",\n    \"Lucknow\",\n    \"+9191840562195\",\n    \"Indian\",\n    \"Sofia Rossi\",\n    \"Rome\",\n    \"+390612345678\",\n    \"Italian\"\n]\n\n# Scan the structured data\nresults = pii_scanner.scan(data=data, chunk_size=10, sample_size=1.0)\n\n# Print the results\nprint(results)\n\n```\n\n\n## Output \n\n```bash\n[\n    {\n        \"text\": \"Ankit Gupta\",\n        \"entity_detected\": [\n            {\"type\": \"PERSON\", \"start\": 0, \"end\": 11, \"score\": 0.85}\n        ]\n    },\n    {\n        \"text\": \"Rome\",\n        \"entity_detected\": [\n            {\"type\": \"LOCATION\", \"start\": 0, \"end\": 4, \"score\": 0.85}\n        ]\n    },\n    {\n        \"text\": \"+919140562195\",\n        \"entity_detected\": [\n            {\"type\": \"PHONE_NUMBER\", \"start\": 0, \"end\": 13, \"score\": 0.85}\n        ]\n    },\n    {\n        \"text\": \"Sofia Rossi\",\n        \"entity_detected\": [\n            {\"type\": \"PERSON\", \"start\": 0, \"end\": 11, \"score\": 0.85}\n        ]\n    },\n    {\n        \"text\": \"Indian\",\n        \"entity_detected\": [\n            {\"type\": \"NATIONALITY\", \"start\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"score\": 0.9}\n        ]\n    }\n]\n\n\n```\n\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "pii_scanner.scanner", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "pii_scanner.scanner.run_async_scan", "asynchronous": true, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Run asynchronous scan"]}], "variables": [{"name": "pii_scanner.scanner.pii_scanner", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pii_scanner.scanner.data", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "pii_scanner.scanner.PIIScanner", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "pii_scanner.scanner.PIIScanner.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pii_scanner.scanner.PIIScanner.scan", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file_path", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "data", "type": {"name": "list", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.list", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "region", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Asynchronous method to scan data or file for PII."]}, {"name": "pii_scanner.scanner.PIIScanner.files_data_pii_scanner_async", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file_path", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "region", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Asynchronous method to process file data for PII.", "Placeholder for file processing methods"]}, {"name": "pii_scanner.scanner.PIIScanner.files_data_pii_scanner", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name"